Output demo/interactive.gif
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Padding 40

Type "./golem"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 2s
Type "/help"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 2s
Type "/clear"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

# copy-safe
Sleep 2s
Type "copy all .md files from demo/fixtures/projects into a new folder called demo/fixtures/projects-dump/docs"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

# Final copy confirmation
Sleep 3s
Type "y"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 3s
Type "/exit"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 2s
